Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: First weeks of Carter presidency
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407bsx
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Feb 1977
The Carter family moves into the White House en masse. Changes made to the previous White House regime. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less